haReport:
This mission was flown by:
Kmdr Patrik Schorner
Ltn Johann Hanneman
Ltn Luther Schaumann

 The mission was flown from Balatre aerodrome.

Successes include the following: 
On 29/07/1916 near Witry-les-Reims.
A F.E.2b of Esc 227 was brought down by Ernst Charles Behm of Jasta 16b.
Cpl Urbain Ternois was killed in action.
S/Lt Blaize Bourgeois was killed in action.
Ernst Charles Behm was  flying a Halberstadt D.II.
